CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1945, pg. 17, reads: "Crawford Aces - Jose Colas, left, and Willie Rowe, Pittsburgh Crawford Aces, who are having a great season with the local club...  Rowe is the team's leading pitcher."
TitMainTitle: Three Pittsburgh Crawfords baseball players, from left: Willie Rowe, possibly Fred Morefield, and unknown, at Forbes Field
